Class DefaultImSessionManager<K,V extends ImSession>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.im.session.DefaultImSessionManager<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the connection type (e.g. IMC or IMV connection)
    V - the session type (e.g. IMC or IMV session)
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImSessionManager<K,V>

    public class DefaultImSessionManager<K,V extends ImSession>
extends Object
implements ImSessionManager<K,V>
    Default session manager. It holds all sessions and manages them according to their state.
